high_descs: Turn left then head to the stove

Open the fridge then put in and out the bowl then close the fridge

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove top.
Pick up the pot on the right of the stove top.
Turn around and walk forward across the room to the refrigerator on the right.
Put the pot in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator doors.
Turn around and walk to the green dining table.
Put the pot on the left side of the dining table, behind the yellow plate.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pot on a dining table.
